SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[AssignedDate], [t].[IdOfVendors], [t].[NameOfVendors], [t].[Optionals], [o].[Id], [o].[ContractId], [o].[OrderedAsset], [o].[Quantity]
FROM (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[AssignedDate], [c].[IdOfVendors], [c].[NameOfVendors], [c].[Optionals]
    FROM [Contract] AS [c]
    WHERE 0 = 1
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [OrderedAssetType] AS [o] ON [t].[Id] = [o].[ContractId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]
